---
title: "US36 — Personalised AI summaries"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Premium User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>HistoryScreen (AI sheet)
  participant C as «Control»<br/>SummariseProgress
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>WorkoutSession · FitnessGoal
  A->>B: tap AI summary
  B->>C: summarise()
  C->>E: summariseProgress(range)
  alt summary returned
    E-->>C: ProgressSummary (personalised, model tag)
    C-->>B: state = AsyncData (tailored text)
    B-->>A: summary, labelled "AI-assisted — not medical advice"
  else AI unavailable
    E-->>C: error
    C-->>B: state = AsyncError
    B-->>A: friendly error, retry
  end
  note over E: summariseProgress via AiGateway → summarise-progress<br/>Edge Function — Premium = personalised vs basic generic (US18a)
